<title>             # introduction title
    Your name is... <strong><%= @character.name %></strong> <br/>
    and you are a <i><%= @character.race %></i>. <br />
</title>

<p>                 # stats paragraph
  <strong>Stats:</strong> <br/>
  Strength:
  <%= @character.strength %> <br/>
  Dexterity:
  <%= @character.dexterity %> <br/>
  Constitution:
  <%= @character.constitution %> <br/>
  Intelligence:
  <%= @character.intelligence %> <br/>
  Wisdom:
  <%= @character.wisdom %> <br/>
  Charisma:
  <%= @character.charisma %> <br/>
</p>

<p>                 # equipment paragraph
    <strong>Equipment:</strong> <br />
    You are profecient in <%= @character.armorClass %> and in your pockets you find <%= @character.gold %> GP.<br />
</p>